name: eupatilin
namespace: chebi_ontology
alt_id: CHEBI:65882
def: "A trimethoxyflavone that is flavone substituted by hydroxy groups at C-5 and C-7 and methoxy groups at C-6, C-3' and C-4' respectively. Isolated from <em>Citrus reticulata</em> and <em>Salvia tomentosa</em>, it exhibits anti-inflammatory, anti-ulcer and antineoplastic activities." []
