def: "A limonoid with formula C<small><sub>28</sub></small>H<small><sub>34</sub></small>O<small><sub>9</sub></small>. It is commonly found in edible citrus fruits including lemons, limes, oranges, and grapefruits. The compound exhibits a variety of biological and pharmacological activities including anticancer, antiinflammatory, antiobesity, and antiviral." []
